@page "/docs/customization/layout"
@namespace LumexUI.Docs.Pages
@layout DocsContentLayout

<DocsSection Title="Overview">
    <p>
        LumexUI’s layout configuration allows you to fine-tune the design of the components.
        You can customize key properties such as typography, border radius, and shadows.
        Additionally, you can define the opacity levels for disabled, focused, hovered, and divider elements,
        providing you with full control over your application's layout and visual consistency.
    </p>

    <Callout Variant="@CalloutVariant.Info">
        Typography and shadows were specifically defined for the customization of
        components and may differ from the default settings provided by Tailwind CSS for similar configurations.
    </Callout>
</DocsSection>

<DocsSection Title="Default Configuration">
    <p>Below are the default layout configuration settings.</p>

    <DocsSection Title="Font Size">
        <Preview>
            <div class="grid gap-8">
                <div>
                    <span class="font-medium text-sm text-foreground-500 font-mono mb-3">text-tiny</span>
                    <p class="text-tiny font-medium text-foreground-900">How vexingly quick daft zebras jump!</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <span class="font-medium text-sm text-foreground-500 font-mono mb-3">text-small</span>
                    <p class="text-small font-medium text-foreground-900">How vexingly quick daft zebras jump!</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <span class="font-medium text-sm text-foreground-500 font-mono mb-3">text-medium</span>
                    <p class="text-medium font-medium text-foreground-900">How vexingly quick daft zebras jump!</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <span class="font-medium text-sm text-foreground-500 font-mono mb-3">text-large</span>
                    <p class="text-large font-medium text-foreground-900">How vexingly quick daft zebras jump!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </Preview>
        <CodeSnippet Code="@(new CodeBlock(name: null, snippet: "layoutConfigFontSizeExample"))" />
        <CodeSnippet Code="@(new CodeBlock(name: "LayoutConfig.cs", snippet: "layoutConfigFontSize"))" />
    </DocsSection>

